tags.description: Wind and rain protected small cave sleeping for about 3 people.
two small caves. suitable for cover in rain and sleeping for about 2-4 people.
Two caves, one about 50m deep. Suitable as shelter for rain and wind. Sleeping possible but at least the bigger one habitated by bats so be responsible!
The water is intended for backpackers, for drinking only.
